name: MyRoommate

”Alexa, open my roommate”
”Alexa, start my roommate”
skdetail:
Rated: Guidance Suggested. This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: my roommate
des:
Use this skill to ask about the house rules and hear contact information (email, phone, address) for the landlord and other important contacts. You can also use the skill to find out how things work (How do I connect to Wi-Fi?) or where to find important items (Where is the plunger?).
This skill was created using a Skill Blueprint. Your requests to this skill are not shared with the skill developer.
